Ralph Grutzmacher, Mayor 01/01/2013 – 12/31/2014 rgrutzmacher@cityoftoledo.org Jack Dunaway 01/01/2010 – 12/31/2014 jdunaway@cityoftoledo.org Jill Lyon 01/01/2013 – 12/31/2016 jlyon@cityoftoledo.org Terri Strom, Council President 01/01/2010 – 12/31/2014 tstrom@cityoftoledo.org Michele Johnson 01/01/2010 – 12/31/2014 mjohnson@cityoftoledo.org Alma Baxter 01/01/2013 – 12/31/2016 abaxter@cityoftoledo.org Jackie Kauffman 01/01/2013 – 12/31/2016 jkauffman@cityoftoledo.org

The Toledo City Council meetings are a good source of information about what is happening in Toledo. Please drop by for a session and see what the council members do to try and make Toledo a better place to live, work and play. The Toledo City Hall Council Chambers is handicapped accessible.

The Toledo City Council meets on the first and third Wednesday of every month at 7:00 pm and the second Tuesday of every month at 6:15 pm in the City Hall Council Chambers. However, this schedule is subject to change. For up to date information, please contact Toledo City Hall at 541-336-2247.
